➜满分作文“不说人话”，高考到底想选拔什么人才？
http://www.sohu.com/a/412193527_115479	1532
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'208647085',
width: '500',
height: '375',
autoplay: false,
